sentences: Thomas Ingamells (born 24 October 1982), better known by his stage name Tom Staar, is an English DJ and record producer.

In 2013, Staar started his own imprint entitled Staar Traxx.
Many of his singles remain for several consecutive weeks in the top 100 on downloading platform Beatport, including "Totem", "Jericho", or "Wide Awake" and "Bora".
